description: This is a quick and delicious roast for those who love lamb.
name: Herb Crusted Rack Of Lamb Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1000g rack of lamb, frenched and scored

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 220°C/200°C fanforced. In a food processor, pulse the olive oil, garlic, bread crumbs, flat leaf parsley, parmesan cheese, rosemary and salt. Rub the mustard all over the lamb rack and cover it with the bread crumb paste.
Roast the lamb until it reaches internal temperature of 55 degrees Celsius about 2025 minutes, Rest for 10 minutes before serving.
